Zondo Commission continues to hear Denel-related testimony * Editor's note: This live event has ended. You may watch a recording above. JOHANNESBURG - The State Capture Commission of Inquiry will continue hearing testimony from Denel. Martin Drevin, Hendrik Johannes Christoffel Van Den Heever and Carene Geldenhuis are set to take the stand. This week, the commission heard of how the Guptas allegedly captured the State-Owned arms company.